---
title: Creamy Mushroom and Beyond Meat® Soup with Truffle Salt and Cheesy Herb and Garlic Toast
description: Lap up luxury with this creamy, truffle-scented Beyond Meat® soup! Savoury mushrooms drink up all the richness and deep flavours of cream, leeks and fragrant truffle salt. Not sold yet? There's also cheesy garlic and herb ciabatta toast to dip and dunk!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soupe-cremeuse-aux-champignons-et-au-beyond-meat-79409ca9.jpg
